overview: A beautiful young lady who does not believe in loving a man but believes that once his pocket is overflowing with money then the man becomes her "Meal ticket". She has always been so successful in this mission of hers until she meets her match and she is stuck with him forever without a penny! Catch the excitement in this comedy filled movie "WHOSE MEAL TICKET" Starring-Akin lewis, lisa omoriodon, ngozi nwosu, uti, Tana adelana, femi durojaye, shaffy bello - my9jatv.com
title: whose meal ticket
